trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Define uma classe base abstrata para definições de parte combináveis, que descrevem e habilitam a criação de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of a part that the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> describes.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância de uma parte que o <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> descreve.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Tipos derivados que substituem este método devem retornar uma nova instância de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objeto toda vez que o método é chamado e nunca deve retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> que descrevem os objetos exportados pela parte definida por este objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objects created by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition" /> objetos que descrevem os objetos exportados fornecidos pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objetos criados pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objetos criados pelo <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> não fornecer objetos exportados, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> coleção em vez disso.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> que descrevem as importações exigidas pela parte definida por este objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objects that describe the imports required by <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objects created by the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition" /> objetos que descrevem as importações exigidas pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart" /> objetos criados pelo <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade nunca devem retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objetos criados pelo <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> não tiver importações, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> coleção em vez disso.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma coleção dos metadados para este objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção que contém os metadados para o <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é vazio, somente leitura <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary`2" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Substituições dessa propriedade devem retornar somente leitura <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objeto com uma comparação não linguística, diferencia maiusculas de minúsculas, como <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>e nunca deve retornar `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> não contém metadados, retornar vazio <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objeto em vez disso.
